<author>ʿạdl smyr, mạjd ʿạdl</author>
<title>ạfrḥ yạ sẖʿb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạfrḥ yạ sẖʿb ạlmsyḥ sẖq sḥạb ạlsmạ bjnạḥk
 ạʿln ḥq ạllh ạlkạml ạsẖhd llkwn ʿn ạ̹ymạnk
 ạlqrạr- mạyhmksẖ wạwʿy̱ tkẖạf mạtqwlsẖ ạ̹n ạ̹ḥnạ ḍʿạf
 rbk ḥạḍr rbk qạdr wfy wsṭ ạlạ̉zmạt ytsẖạf
 2- mhmạ tqạbl sẖdẗ wḍyq fy ạsmh tlạqy ḥṣn ạ̉mạnk
 wʿdh fy ḍʿfk hạyqwyk zy ạlnsr yrd sẖbạbk
 3- mhmạ kẖywṭ ạlsẖms tdwb fy qlb ạlʿtmẗ wsṭ nhạrk
 ḥqk zy ạlḍhr ybạn wmạfysẖ qwẗ thz slạmk</lyrics>
</song>